    "about_values": {
      "type": "split-content",
      "settings": {
        "balance": "right-heavy",
        "sticky_column": "left",
        "color_scheme": "standard-secondary",
        "top_spacing": "auto",
        "bottom_spacing": "auto"
      },
      "blocks": {
        "values_eyebrow": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>How we work</p>",
            "size": "sm",
            "uppercase": true,
            "muted": true,
            "position": "left"
          }
        },
        "values_heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Three commitments that shape everything we do.",
            "size": "4xl",
            "position": "left"
          }
        },
        "values_1_title": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Small named teams.",
            "size": "xl",
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
        "values_1_body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>You don't call a pool of rotating engineers. You call three people by name, and they already know your stack, your vendors, and the room your server lives in.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "uppercase": false,
            "muted": false,
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
        "values_2_title": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Portable documentation.",
            "size": "xl",
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
        "values_2_body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Your environment is documented in a system you can read and export at any time. If you leave, you walk out with everything a competent successor needs. We don't hold knowledge hostage.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "uppercase": false,
            "muted": false,
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
        "values_3_title": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Plain-language reporting.",
            "size": "xl",
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
        "values_3_body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Quarterly reviews written for an office manager, not a network engineer. What broke, what we fixed, what to budget for next quarter — in sentences you'd read aloud at a partner meeting.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "uppercase": false,
            "muted": false,
            "position": "right"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": ["values_eyebrow", "values_heading", "values_1_title", "values_1_body", "values_2_title", "values_2_body", "values_3_title", "values_3_body"]
